---
import HeroButton from './HeroButton.astro';
---

<div class="text-white">
  <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">
    Boost Support Efficiency & Elevate Customer Experience with AI
  </h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    Get instant, 24/7 sales and support from an AI trained on your content. Free up your team.
  </p>
  <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-lg text-white/80">
    <li class="flex items-center">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
      <span>An AI chatbot that deeply understands both your offerings and customer needs.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-center">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
      <span>Sales and support rolled into one, available 24/7</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-center">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
      <span>Expertly guides users from purchase consideration to post-sale support.</span>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Recommendation 4: Add Social Proof (Logos, Testimonials) near here on the actual page -->

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
    <HeroButton href="/contact" variant="primary">
      Get Started with a Free 7-Day Trial
    </HeroButton>

  </div>
</div>